Here on the Major Issues Podcast, we pride ourselves in covering the LATEST and GREATEST things to come to comic books and comic book media. What happens when certain films are centered on Superheroes but not based on any comic? You get this very special episode where we tackle some of the best and worst superhero movies not based on a particular comic book! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

